    <h1>Legacy configuration injection</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>For better integration between 5.x (symfony based) kernel and legacy (4.=
x) kernel, injection is used to inject settings, <a href=3D"/display/EZP/Le=
gacy+session+injection">session</a> and <a href=3D"/display/EZP/Legacy+site=
access+injection">current siteaccess</a> from 5.x into legacy using an even=
t:&nbsp;<span class=3D"nv" style=3D"color: rgb(0,128,128);"><a href=3D"/dis=
play/EZP/Legacy+kernel+event">kernel.event_subscriber</a></span></p>
<p><span class=3D"nv" style=3D"color: rgb(0,128,128);"><style type=3D"text/=
css">/*<![CDATA[*/
div.rbtoc1485853399423 {padding: 0px;}
div.rbtoc1485853399423 ul {list-style: disc;margin-left: 0px;}
div.rbtoc1485853399423 li {margin-left: 0px;padding-left: 0px;}

/*]]>*/</style></span></p>
<div class=3D"toc-macro rbtoc1485853399423">=20
<ul class=3D"toc-indentation">=20
<li><a href=3D"#Legacyconfigurationinjection-Injectedsettings">Injected set=
tings</a>=20
<ul class=3D"toc-indentation">=20
<li><a href=3D"#Legacyconfigurationinjection-Databasesettings">Database set=
tings</a></li>=20
<li><a href=3D"#Legacyconfigurationinjection-Storagesettings">Storage setti=
ngs</a></li>=20
<li><a href=3D"#Legacyconfigurationinjection-Imagesettings">Image settings<=
/a></li>=20
<li><a href=3D"#Legacyconfigurationinjection-UsingImageMagickfilters">Using=
 ImageMagick filters</a></li>=20
<li><a href=3D"#Legacyconfigurationinjection-Extendinginjectedsettings">Ext=
ending injected settings</a></li>=20
<li><a href=3D"#Legacyconfigurationinjection-Sitesettings">Site settings</a=
></li>=20
</ul> </li>=20
<li><a href=3D"#Legacyconfigurationinjection-InjectedBehavior">Injected&nbs=
p;Behavior</a>=20
<ul class=3D"toc-indentation">=20
<li><a href=3D"#Legacyconfigurationinjection-eZFormToken(CSRF)integration">=
eZFormToken (CSRF) integration</a></li>=20
