<h3 id=3D"Legacyconfigurationinjection-UsingImageMagickfilters">Using Image=
Magick filters</h3>
<p>The following block shows a valid ImageMagick filter usage example for <=
code>ezpublish.yml</code>:</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl" style=3D"border-bottom-width: 1px=
;">
<b>ImageMagick filters usage example</b>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">=20
<pre class=3D"brush: php; gutter: false; theme: Eclipse" style=3D"font-size=
:12px;">ezpublish:
    imagemagick:
        filters:
            geometry/scale: "-geometry {1}x{2}"</pre>=20
</div>
</div>
<p>Since ImageMagick filter usage changed from eZ Publish 4.x versions you =
can find the list of filters existing by default to use eZ Publish 5.x:</p>
